    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is ready for a new owner who appreciates a reliable workhorse with some character. The exterior shows typical signs of age, including some paint fading on the roof and hood, along with various small dings and surface scratches. Inside, the cabin is functional but shows wear on the driver's seat and some aging of the plastic trim. Mechanically, it runs and drives fine, though it would benefit from a tune-up and some minor suspension work in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car for someone looking for a budget-friendly option.",
      "price": 19800.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
