    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its ownership. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts precisely, making it a dependable choice for daily commuting or long-distance travel. While the exterior is generally clean, you may find a few minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with normal use. The interior is well-preserved, with all electronics functioning as intended and only minimal wear on the driver's seat bolster. Overall, this is a solid, reliable car that is ready for its next owner with no immediate repairs needed.",
      "price": 35000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this fantastic find! This car is in truly good condition, offering a smooth, reliable ride and a clean, well-cared-for interior that shows just how much it's been loved. It\u2019s a solid, dependable vehicle that\u2019s ready for many more miles of adventures. You won't find a better balance of quality and value!",
      "price": 34500.0,
